[ ] - Register alerts: The user should be able to register a stock alert with a 
max amount of sales and a min amount of purchase.
[ ] - Delete alerts: The user should be able to delete a specific stock alert.
[ ] - List stock alerts: The should be able to see all your stock alerts.
[ ] - Stock notification: The application must send a notification by email 
for each user, notifying about stocks updates.
[ ] - Auth with captcha: The application must enforce authentication with captcha 
to protect users informations.
